title: tour: some errors on the spanish version
body: Following https://github.com/golang/go/issues/9090#issuecomment-196977535: > This translate error are present on the tour yet, > > `Observa que el tipo de indica [...]` must be `Observa que el tipo se indica[...]` and more. > > ---------- > > ---------- > > [This changes](https://github.com/rcostu/go-tour-es/pull/11/commits/31bab96b22a6ddae30de587432291f2bee480566 ) are gone at sometime. > _First errors found on https://go-tour-es.appspot.com/#7_ The Spanish version have some typos again. I'm newbie with Go and its community so I'll be happy if you tell me where I can fix this typos on the repo to make a pull request with all typos that I can find through the tour.
